{"tid":994819,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習權時代】私立幼兒園將全變公立 內地家長：方便洗腦","createTime":"2019-01-25T03:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T04:02:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d6dba5c8abfa625271f6088df79dbb2c0f52a8d","tid":994819,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"國務院周二(22日)發佈《關於開展城鎮小區配套幼兒園治理工作的通知》（以下簡稱：該《通知》），強調要着力構建以普惠性資源為主體的學前教育公共服務體系，不得辦營利性幼兒園(即香港的幼稚園)。通知要求今年4月底前，完成對各地幼兒園的全面摸底排查。山東一所公立幼兒園工作人員表示，公立幼兒園使用政府教育局提供的教材，私立幼兒園則使用自編教材。<br />\n該《通知》強調，要着力構建以普惠性資源為主體的學前教育公共服務體系，小區配套幼兒園應由當地教育行政部門辦成公辦幼兒園，或委託辦成普惠性民辦幼兒園，不得辦成營利性幼兒園。該《通知》稱，各地以縣（市、區）為單位，對城鎮小區配套幼兒園進行全面摸底排查，列出清單，要於本年4月底前完成。《通知》還要求已建成的小區配套幼兒園，應按照規定在限期前移交給當地教育行政部門。<br />\n內地各地幼兒園目前分為兩類，一是政府教育系統所辦的幼兒園、特殊行業辦幼兒園、公辦高校附屬幼兒園、企事業單位辦幼兒園等多種形式的公辦幼兒園；另一類是私立幼兒園。公辦幼兒園是由政府或企事業單位的資金投入，佔運營成本主要部份。民辦幼兒園的教師則以質素高，教學能力強見稱，收費也相對較高，受中產家庭歡迎。<br />\n對於政府以補貼幼兒園為手段，逐漸取締私立幼兒園，山東臨沂一所公立幼兒園的員工盧女士表示，私立幼兒園有其特色，吸引不少家庭。但公立幼兒園的教材帶有宣傳愛國主義教育成份：「私立幼兒園能辦出特色，它才能營利，所以對思想領域，對洗腦方面，肯定不會太注重。...第二，幼兒園轉型，由私立變為公立，說實在就是為了方便洗腦。把小孩放在一條流水線上，開始洗腦。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190125/large/1548382191_13f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190125%2Flarge%2F1548382191_13f0.jpg&h=4cf6cfe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190125/59182893\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190125%2F59182893&d=0R25PRPV8%2Bl%2F0TdEluToSlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=6ffd8558\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190125%2F59182893&h=c42803ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190125/59182893</a>"},{"pid":"47dc26a0f4ba81d656d235a55852f68c101bf84e","tid":994819,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:50:32.000Z","msg":"我們今天看看故事書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n習近平的現代社會主義思想"},{"pid":"ec2cb189f9d247f655ba1c6ba536d6aa611902b4","tid":994819,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"中國香港呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76143f51ce86cd6e2bdf3cbc3bb1df787322ce34","tid":994819,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec2cb189f9d247f655ba1c6ba536d6aa611902b4","tid":994819,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"中國香港呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:59:11.000Z","msg":"普教中"},{"pid":"b54ab7fee9b51611d9f1721bc4dfb3489d663396","tid":994819,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76143f51ce86cd6e2bdf3cbc3bb1df787322ce34","tid":994819,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec2cb189f9d247f655ba1c6ba536d6aa611902b4","tid":994819,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"中國香港呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class